import React from "react"
import Head from "next/head"
import AppLayout from "../components/AppLayout"
import NicknamedEditForm from "../components/NicknamedEditForm"
import FollowList from "../components/FollowList"

const Profile = () => {
  const followerList = [
    { nickname: 'seolranlee' },
    { nickname: 'zerocho' },
    { nickname: 'nodebird' }
  ]

  const followingList = [
    { nickname: 'seolranlee' },
    { nickname: 'zerocho' },
    { nickname: 'nodebird' }
  ]
  return (
    <>
      <Head>
        <title>내 프로필 | NodeBird</title>
      </Head>
      <AppLayout>
        <NicknamedEditForm />
        <FollowList header="팔로잉 목록" followingList={followingList} />
        <FollowList header="팔로워 목록" followerList={followerList} />
      </AppLayout>
    </>
  )
}

export default Profile
